VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(urllib2|socket)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(connect|send|recv|urlopen|request) && MISSING:(timeout=|ssl|TLS|verify=True|cert_reqs)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of network-related modules urllib2 and socket in Python code.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Network Calls: urllib2 and socket.
